videos.description: Great ball movement by Wake Forest results in Ismael Massoud feeding Jahcobi Neath for a 3-pointer.

videos.description: With 7.8 seconds left in the game, Xavier's Quentin Goodin misses the game winning 3-pointer and Wake Forest wins 80-78.
